curam.util.client.model
Interface ContainerBuilder

All Superinterfaces:
ComponentBuilder<Container>, java.io.Serializable
public interface ContainerBuilder
extends ComponentBuilder<Container>

A builder for containers. The builder simplifies the details of the construction process and ensures that an appropriate implementation of the container is provided.

copyShallow

void copyShallow(Container container)
Copies the properties of the given container to the container being built. This operates in the same manner as the ComponentBuilder.copy(Component) method, except that the children of the container are not copied. This allows the children to be filtered or copied-and-modified before being added to the copy of the original container.

Parameters:
container - The container to be copied. It is ignored if it is null. Child components will not be copied.
